quest.name: Save Rasheed - Spatial 2018
quest.intro:
A few months ago, Rasheed was on a geocache hike and he was abducted by aliens. Rasheed escaped, but not without being tested with radioactive materials beforehand! Rasheed made it back to Earth safely, but now his beard has grown quite a bit! It glows green when he is sleeping, and he occasionally sleepwalks. Sometimes, he will sleepwalk all the way across the state of California!

Whenever he sleepwalks, aliens will arrive at his last known location. They still need to do more tests and want to abduct him again!

Click the "Quest Log" below to view your first quest to Save Rasheed.
quest.description: Save Rasheed (and his beerd) whilest he battles ALIENS and sleep walks through San Diego!

checkins.name: Broadway Pier
checkins.description: If you “peer” into the distance, you think you can see some more UFOs over the water… better move fast if you want to find Rasheed!
checkins.hint: Take a stroll down the boardwalk

checkins.name: Unconditional Surrender Statue
checkins.description: You must not surrender to the aliens - Rasheed is unconditionally counting on you!

checkins.name: Star of India
checkins.description: Built in 1863, this restored iron-hulled windjammer is now a secret-hideout "museum" for the XYO Network that occasionally sails across the stars and delivers crazy location data!!

checkins.name: Waterfront Park Fountain
checkins.description: It looks like there’s wet footprints along the concrete… Is Rasheed sleepbathing now too?!

checkins.name: Santa Fe Depot
checkins.description: Did you know that Rasheed once wandered onto the train and ended up all the way in La Jolla? Luckily, he swung by the local pancake place and got himself some breakfast before heading back home.
checkins.hint: Look at it from across the street to get that picture.
